{"tid":1990361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「正視聽」屎生從來唔撚係同路人","createTime":"2020-04-26T15:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T16:20:15.000Z","uid":79589,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4eaec09f6373ab804b70718ccbd448b443065949","tid":1990361,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:24:28.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 周庭條新片正顯示分化主義嘅禍害<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1989675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1989675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隔離Post 屌觀眾將重點轉移左去舊屎到，偏離主題<br />\n然後就怪人分化，甚至覺得段片有舊屎係到先可以擴大觀眾群<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">屌你老母啦！舊屎只係趁機撈油食人血饅頭，從來都唔撚係同路人！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 成件事就係周庭缺乏政治觸角，搵左一個錯誤嘅人<br />\n<br />\n2. 舊屎由始至終都只係想借運動撈油水，呃手足食人血饅頭，屌佢就係唔撚想有手足比佢屎呃到，損失慘重<br />\n<br />\n3. 成件事就係捉老鼠入米缸，分分鐘因為舊屎搞臭成個圈。唔通你想見到有手足因為信舊屎比佢呃撚左出嚟搞個苦主大聯盟？"},{"pid":"e248f28fc97f941570036488ab33f2e71ec59f1f","tid":1990361,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:27:44.000Z","msg":"你123點冇解釋到屎生點解唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n只係講緊如果佢係藍絲嘅禍害"},{"pid":"dcce3090ef92350900a2dc865ce65499146a613f","tid":1990361,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d09f0840b83cfbed2eaac84d3ed9df84b054cc1e","tid":1990361,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:28:00.000Z","msg":"觸覺啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觸角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset